data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. MOTIVATED SELLER!!! BRING YOUR OFFER!!!Seller will Help with CLOSING COSTS Beautiful Property with 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms recently renovated, the owner kept the property in such a way that when you visit it you think you are in a new property, with many improvements inside and outside the property, perfectly prepared for your main property is everything a first-time buyer is looking for, an unbeatable location close to Disney World, Universal Studios, Sea World, the airport and a wide range of restaurants, and shopping centers where it allows you to connect with all the main thoroughfares. The beautiful community, With an incredibly low HOA fee, this is a great opportunity where you can get all the benefits of the first buyer and if you are an investor you will achieve the best profitability by generating constant income. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own an incredible property. Submit your offer now!
